    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://karlivare.com/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 15:14:46 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://karlivare.com/about/</guid>
      <description>Hi, I&amp;rsquo;m Karli! I’m a designer focused on crafting thoughtful digital experiences across web, marketing, and social media. I’m especially drawn to digital storytelling and capturing emotional states through branding and expressive, intentional design. My work balances minimalism and clarity with a playful edge, creating experiences that feel clean, intuitive, and human.
With a background in front-end development, I approach design with both creativity and technical awareness. Understanding how things are built has made me a more strategic designer and a self-proclaimed “troubleshooting queen” who isn’t afraid to dig deep (even if that means finding a YouTube video with 10 views) to master new tools and solve complex problems.</description>
